data.description: Seller credit to buyers for $7,500 in closing costs at closing! Acreage near Lake Lowell with a ton of potential. Just over an acre and comes with a large barn with power. Perfect for animals/horse set up. 3 bed, 2 bath home comes with a separate room attached by the carport. Currently used as a perfect storage/office area or add plumbing. It could become a separate living quarters. Also with the property is an RV pad that already has a second electric meter. The previous owner was able to rent the RV hookup to create extra income. Not too many opportunities to get an acre and a half near Lake Lowell, so don’t miss out.
